.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftwgirlsganhwa%2Fposts%2F3321155384667111&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9jKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=2896b1fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/twgirlsganhwa/posts/3321155384667111</a><br />\n<br />\n歌名：我們是朋友<br />\n樂團：群眾樂團 / The Commoner（วงสามัญชน）<br />\n<br />\n若你聽見震耳樂聲，<br />\n你得去呼朋引伴，<br />\n那是群眾們在躁動，<br />\n是和我們一樣普通的人們。<br />\n<br />\n若你聽見隆隆鼓聲，<br />\n那是群眾們在跺腳，<br />\n響徹雲霄，只因自由的人們集結，<br />\n在同一片天空下。<br />\n<br />\n繁星依舊閃耀，<br />\n熠熠在遠方漆黑的夜空，<br />\n將我們的心繫在一塊，<br />\n堅定信仰，直到我們戰勝的那天。<br />\n<br />\n以鼓掌發出鼓聲，<br />\n發誓不會讓誰，<br />\n來侵犯、剝奪自由的權利，<br />\n只要我們還有一口氣在。<br />\n<br />\n攜手一同向前，<br />\n我們是朋友。"},{"pid":"212b343f55b739f873419211a93e18ec5261a679","tid":2214423,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b451d3e5fd2a2ed93e644bb749d37f52363bb50f","tid":2214423,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"回覆#10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6954a5e37d3b5b201bad15f42d8a62a951c55066","tid":2214423,"uid":231912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f5698b6665e48bbc7b77177096be870dacf1128","tid":2214423,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"【德國戰線】【官方聯署！】鄺頌晴：儲齊50,000個簽名，召開制裁中國嘅聽證會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2214595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2214595</a>"},{"pid":"310bfbff2ce02afc3474220c5405967ba9230b0f","tid":2214423,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但泰國人唔係應該反軍政府先啱咩？<br />\n國王好似無咩實權"},{"pid":"c4e8db5fa01184ba1b23538b21421f5124fbf1eb","tid":2214423